{
  "stem": "19969.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 185.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "As I had it then-- with a reinforced company, I had about 200 men, a little over 200 men.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the post was very large.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It covered well over a hundred acres-- I guess several hundred acres.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we first got into it, what we found-- the left unit, with the company commander, they got into warehouse areas and maintenance buildings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There were a great number of buildings in there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There were barracks, supply-- great stores of supplies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when I went over the wall, I found myself in the back of a-- of a very beautiful home, which I immediately assumed were officers' homes.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I yelled at my two men, be careful of booby traps!",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We did not encounter any, I might add, at any time in Dachau.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But I went in the back door of this home with my two men.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I looked around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we walked in carefully and walked through the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was empty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But in one bedroom, I found children's toys scattered on the floor and great signs of disarray, like hasty packing had been done.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they-- this family, this German family-- officer family had left.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So looking at that, I knew immediately that probably many of the officers or most of them had fled the area.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were all SS officers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The concentration camps were strictly SS people and Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I immediately assumed that when I saw this hasty evacuation that the camp had been at least partially evacuated.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we walked in carefully-- and I went out the front door of this home.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I found myself in a beautifully landscaped area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was like a small city, you know, paved roads, flower-- roses were blooming or starting to bloom, as I recall.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
